         <h2 class="about_h2">About</h2>

    <p>2024 marks the 5th edition of Karrusel. Karrusel is a circus themed rave  presenting some of the world's leading electronic artists. 

Past  editions include performances by Acid Pauli, Amelie Lens, Dixon, FJAAK,
  Folamour, Hunee, Job Jobse, Kölsch, Mall Grab, Nastia, Partiboi69, Peggy  Gou,
   Richie Hawtin, Skin On Skin, The Blessed Madonna, Victor Ruiz and  VTSS.
    The festival is open air and takes place on secluded green spot at  the abandoned
     shipyard of Refshaleøen in central Copenhagen.</p>
    </div>
   
